<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Homeserver 2027 Portal</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --paper: #f4efe4;
      --line: #d8d1c2;
      --accent: #0f766e;
      --glow: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.18);
    }
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: "Noto Sans", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, var(--glow), transparent 32%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f3ea 0%, #ece5d7 100%);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    main {
      width: min(980px, 100%);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 2.4rem;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0 0 2rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 50rem;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    a {
      display: block;
      padding: 1.15rem;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95));
      transition: transform 120ms ease, box-shadow 120ms ease;
    }
    a:hover,
    a:focus {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.14);
      outline: none;
    }
    strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    }
    .url {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      opacity: 0.78;
      word-break: break-word;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <h1>Homeserver 2027</h1>
    <p>Shared internal frontdoor for the local services used by Wolf and Franz. This page is intentionally lightweight and keeps the Surface Go kiosk path consistent before a dedicated portal application exists.</p>
    <section class="grid">
{% for link in toolbox_network_portal_links %}
      <a href="{{ link.url }}">
        <strong>{{ link.label }}</strong>
        <span class="url">{{ link.url }}</span>
      </a>
{% endfor %}
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
